title: An Art-Filled Home in the Hamptons; Art and antique dealers Barbara and Lloyd Macklowe are listing their East Hampton home for $60 million.
text:
The owners moved walls and added windows for more light.

There are doors to the outside from almost every room.

The kitchen.

There are five bedrooms.

A walkway to the beach.

The grounds have Japanese maple, Yoshino cherry and apple trees.

An Art-Filled Home in the Hamptons
